# ~/.config/hwe/packages-aur.lst — the AUR packages YOU want on this machine.
#
# Same format and the same rules as packages.lst, installed with paru instead of
# pacman. HWE bootstraps paru the first time any AUR list is non-empty, so
# naming something here is enough — you do not need a helper installed first.

# visual-studio-code-bin
# spotify
